_sText:
This is version 2 of the BloodMoon map with updates from my
collaboration with clan member Nine.

Side halls and church walls were added to the map.  Along with some ambiance
in soundscapes, flying crows, and blood stains galore.  There are also corner 
sniper perches and some urns to practice your aim on.

The fog in the mausoleum and the quirky red moon have been retained.
